No upgrades, no prestige mechanics, absolutely nothing other than click corn, number go up. You just leave it open in the background to get "drops", which are just jpegs of different colored corn to click on.

Despite having no upgrades or prestige mechanics or anything from other good idle games, it DOES manage to have microtransactions.

A complete waste of time for the download alone. Don't bother.
